messages.content: Hi there! This is Sarah from DreamSeed. What's your full name?

It's jane@williamsmedia.com and this is extremely urgent - I need to launch next week!

Williams Media Corp - we specialize in social media marketing for real estate agents. Based in Miami.
This is URGENT! I have a $75k contract waiting and need my corporation paperwork ASAP.
